{"tid":755983,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"錄影用external hard disk 一問","createTime":"2018-07-25T15:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T03:56:31.000Z","uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62e04aaa184e737aa9e37f48668641080a6c7112","tid":755983,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"想請問如果買專係用來錄電視的external hard disk，邊一隻牌子最好用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSales話最好買插火牛的external hard disk，否則長遠會拖累電視，請問又係唔係真的呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2f6ede98e606b5fc2815c79b21f4318831953a","tid":755983,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e04aaa184e737aa9e37f48668641080a6c7112","tid":755983,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"想請問如果買專係用來錄電視的external hard disk，邊一隻牌子最好用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSales話最好買插火牛的external hard disk，否則長遠會拖累電視，請問又係唔係真的呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"sales係驚唔知你個電視個usb做得好唔好，夠唔夠電流推，外置電安心啲掛，我估。<br />\n不過呢，你都係睇清楚你部電視個spec先，係好屎雞電視，定係smart tv，買太大size認唔到就攪鬼啦。<br />\n<br />\n利申，冇買過，鳩噏。"},{"pid":"75bc4403b08e4acbd82ea6862f66fc2e26837f2e","tid":755983,"uid":147831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:32:26.000Z","msg":"真係最好買外置供電，如果唔係隻hard disk 都好易壞"},{"pid":"d42b28293a9f86e93aba0fff14f811f3467b93e0","tid":755983,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bc4403b08e4acbd82ea6862f66fc2e26837f2e","tid":755983,"uid":147831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:32:26.000Z","msg":"真係最好買外置供電，如果唔係隻hard disk 都好易壞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"有邊隻較為好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e3a2e7ad0cbf86056b54a32